{"lemma":"عُشٌّ","slug":"عُشٌّ","root":"ع.ش.ش","root_slug":"ع-ش-ش","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ش-ش","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n29168"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8F%D8%B4%D9%8C%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"nest"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to stay or keep to one's nest, lair, or home"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to seek, to look for; to acquire, to collect, to gather"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to dislodge, to expel, to take up residence in another's home or territory"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to repair especially of clothes, to keep them in a usable state, to maintain a nest especially said of a bird"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n29168","headword_ar":"عُشٌّ","root":"E$","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nest of a bird, formed of what it collects together,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Mgh, O, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of slender pieces of sticks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O, K,) &c., (S, O,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of fragments of sticks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which it lays its eggs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a tree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Mgh, O, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the branches thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea$~N","text_ar":"عَشٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A, K:) but if in a mountain, (S, O, Msb,) or a building, (Msb,) or a wall or the like, (S, O,) it is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wakorN","text_ar":"وَكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wakonN","text_ar":"وَكْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and if in the ground,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ufoHuwSN","text_ar":"اُفْحُوصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^udoHiY~N","text_ar":"اُدْحِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nest of a raven"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other bird, upon a tree, when it is dense,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compact, and large:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T:) pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEo$aA$N","text_ar":"اَعْشَاشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb) and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei$aA$N","text_ar":"عِشَاشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei$a$apN","text_ar":"عِشَشَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eu$uw$N","text_ar":"عُشُوشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eu$oEu$N","text_ar":"عُشْعُشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] It is said in a prov., quoted in a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTobap","text_ar":"خُطْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of El-Hajjáj, (O, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layosa h`*aA","text_ar":"لَيْسَ هٰذَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biEu$~iki faA@dorujiY","text_ar":"بِعُشِّكِ فَا@دْرُجِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is not thy nest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thou hast no right in this; therefore go thy way:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, O, K: *) addressed to him who alights in a place of abode not befitting him: (A, TA:) or to him who raises himself above his rank: and to him who applies himself to a thing not of his business to do: and to him who is at case in an improper time; wherefore he is thus ordered to be diligent and in motion. (TA.) And in another prov., (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"talam~aso A^aEo$aA$aka","text_ar":"تَلَمَّسْ اَعْشَاشَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Seek thou,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seek thou repeatedly, after pretexts, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"causes for"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"false accusation, in thy family"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and those belonging to thee:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [not in others: (see Freytag's Arab. Prov., i. 235:)] nearly like the former proverb. (TA.) [In the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"talam~asa","text_ar":"تَلَمَّسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"talam~aso","text_ar":"تَلَمَّسْ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Mgh","O","Msb","K","Lth","T","TA","L"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}